{"tid":1821332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全元朗人同我入嚟記住呢個自稱有份參與721嘅女人","createTime":"2020-01-12T07:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T19:26:27.000Z","uid":211994,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"872d7eb73eb9a43f153224b8c64842b212d3eea1","tid":1821332,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T07:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m2P7Xjg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm2P7Xjg.jpg&h=8d367379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1538 #元朗 #元朗警署<br />\n圖中女士為今天遊行的發起人。她認為光復兩字非常殘酷。並有不少「黑衣人」不斷發放文宣「得元朗得天下」。所以元朗市民只能發起身穿白衣保衛元朗。她認為罪魁禍首都是黑衣人以及林卓廷議員，陷害元朗市民令其他人認為元朗市民品格底下。她表示自己亦有參加「白衣人的行動」，當時身在公園。如果沒有罪魁禍首林卓廷何來有白衣人手持藤條襲擊市民。有記者問她當天有沒有手持藤條，她並沒有回應記者的問題。<br />\n<br />\n#HK01<br />\n小編O:咁你洗唔洗自己自首左先?"},{"pid":"2658449525e2cdb89633d4dbfa899af3c8617cf0","tid":1821332,"uid":174013,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T07:53:07.000Z","msg":"個柒樣好似中左幅射咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a9e0b4a491b7f9d7a1676c9ad2648c2a65232f","tid":1821332,"uid":225818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T07:57:37.000Z","msg":"小編又幾串下喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed438a29edef20553186b20807ee3f31060e8fc","tid":1821332,"uid":282384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:13:14.000Z","msg":"有參與姐係拉得喇"},{"pid":"938a83f5626b58aa1660ab0ecc93f75df56f678a","tid":1821332,"uid":271516,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:26:22.000Z","msg":"非法集結 拉得"},{"pid":"a01d9754206d9f589895d537baf10e68f152605e","tid":1821332,"uid":252069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:39:04.000Z","msg":"屌你! 黃色經濟圈根本影響唔到d資源分配!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過無所謂<br />\n因為學波蘭人將抗爭融入生活先係目的</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"